# Welcome to Jaringan

This is a terminal-native page. It stays useful as raw text, but it can also be parsed into semantic blocks for agents and rendered into a TUI for humans.

=> jar://jaringan.local/about About Jaringan
=> https://github.com/thesimonharms/jaringan Source repository placeholder

```plain
AI view: parse headings, paragraphs, links, and actions without screenshots.
Human view: browse with a fast keyboard-first terminal UI.
```
